These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, asparagus, mango, raspberry
1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
3. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | peas | asparagus | mango | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, hot-chocolate, mirinda
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice | lemonade | mirinda | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, filmmaking, magic-tricks, writing
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | hiking | magic-tricks | filmmaking | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, scientific, martial-arts
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | horror | martial-arts | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, handball, climbing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | climbing | handball | parkour | rugby |

