3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | action | fantasy | western |

