.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, tomato, orange, cauliflower
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person eating tomato is between the person eating cranberry and the person eating cauliflower##2
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | cauliflower | tomato | cranberry | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, rat, goldfish
1. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | rat | turtle | frog | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, brazilian, nigerian, egyptian
1. the nigerian is between the egyptian and the brazilian##2
2. the nigerian is on the left of the egyptian##1
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | nigerian | egyptian | canadian |

